Summary: Round spheres to the left and below the moon, many more to the right.
divs: sighting detailsi was on my deck with my dogs, i looked at the moon and there were 7 sphere,s,,, one had a red orb above it tilting back and forth,,, then i saw more to the rigth of the moon,, thought they were baloons but they were way to high up, i went in to get my camera and when i came out they just disapeared,,, i was wondering if anyone else saw then,, i called 2 news channels but they said i was the only one who saw them. i know what i seen was,nt ordinary,,, i,d like to know if anyone else saw them? *(wit's name deleted--sgonzalez\cms).
